Title: Iron Jawed Angels
Writer: Jennifer Friedes (story), Sally Robinson (teleplay), Eugenia Bostwick-Singer (teleplay), Raymond Singer (teleplay), Jennifer Friedes (teleplay)
Actors: Hilary Swank, Margo Martindale, Anjelica Huston, Frances O'Connor
Plot: Defiant young activists take the women's suffrage movement by storm, putting their lives at risk to help American women win the right to vote.
Awards: Won 1 Golden Globe. Another 3 wins & 27 nominations.
